{"tid":1976840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Elon Musk豪爽說要捐贈千台呼吸機 加州州長：過3週 一台都沒收到","createTime":"2020-04-17T13:40:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T15:37:46.000Z","uid":76115,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c844aa50d719f96dc32514c64df323c536b19a16","tid":1976840,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T13:40:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-04-17/393081\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-04-17%2F393081&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU9%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=8e4181e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-04-17/393081</a><br />\n<br />\n根據美國CNN報導，特斯拉公司CEO伊隆&middot;馬斯克3月時允諾捐贈超過1000台呼吸機給美國加州的醫院。加州州長葛文&middot;紐森當時還大讚馬斯克 :「是一種英雄般的行為」。不過加州州長辦公室今天卻表示，到目前為止，一台呼吸器都沒收到。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克3月24日在社交網站上表示，中國的呼吸機供過於求，因此向中國購買了1255台符合美國食品和藥物管理局(FDA)標準的呼吸機，準備捐給家州醫院。<br />\n<br />\n然而，加州州長緊急服務辦公室發言人4月16日表示，至今沒有醫院收到呼吸機。「伊隆&middot;馬斯克和他的團隊告訴政府以採購足量呼吸基捐給醫院。但政府每天與加州的醫院確認供應情況，至今都未收到特斯拉或馬斯克供給的呼吸機。」<br />\n<br />\n對此，馬斯克未做出回應。"},{"pid":"7ba26730c9fa6643bc7cfae749ebe669501ec6f6","tid":1976840,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T13:41:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f2079b0d2efa926b5c636e44276690ec9b76dc","tid":1976840,"uid":78470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T13:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701c40a1834cb0c83fd40e6a58f4d8f54b1bf8a9","tid":1976840,"uid":30040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T13:42:07.000Z","msg":"C朗式慈善<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"